{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-post-container-index-tsx","path":"/next/next-ts/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"nodes":[{"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#setup\">Setup</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-packagejson-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">1. package.json 생성하기</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-package-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">2. 필요한 package 설치하기</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-packagejson%EC%97%90-script-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">3. package.json에 script 추가하기</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#4-public-pages-%ED%8F%B4%EB%8D%94-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">4. public, pages 폴더 생성</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#5-pages-%ED%8F%B4%EB%8D%94%EC%97%90-_apptsx-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">5. pages 폴더에 _app.tsx 파일 생성</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#6-gitignore-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%EF%B8%8F\">6. .gitignore 설정❗️</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#7-eslintrcjson\">7. .eslintrc.json</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#\">??</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#error\">Error</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC\">에러</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\">해결</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#-%EB%81%9D-\">✨ 끝! ✨</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0-%EC%9E%90%EB%A3%8C\">참고 자료</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}],"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p><code class=\"language-text\">create-next-app</code>(CNA)을 사용하지 않고 개발 환경 구축하기 ✨</p>\n<p>최근들어 CRA나 CNA를 사용하지 않고 개발환경을 직접 구축해 보고 싶은 마음이 생겼다. <a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/getting-started\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">공식 문서</a>에도 잘 나와 있지만, 더 쓰기 편하도록 내 나름대로 정리해 봤다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"setup\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#setup\" aria-label=\"setup permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Setup</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-packagejson-생성하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-packagejson-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"1 packagejson 생성하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. package.json 생성하기</h3>\n<p>프로젝트 폴더 생성 후 해당 디렉토리에서 아래 명령어를 실행한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> init <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-y</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-필요한-package-설치하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-package-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"2 필요한 package 설치하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 필요한 package 설치하기</h3>\n<p>TypeScript 기반으로 React와 Next를 사용하기 때문에 필요한 패키지를 설치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> react next react-dom</code></pre></div>\n<p>TypeScript를 사용한다면 아래와같이 <code class=\"language-text\">devDependencies</code>를 추가로 설정한다.\n<code class=\"language-text\">devDependencies</code>로 추가한 아래 모듈들은 배포 시 포함되지 않는다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> <span class=\"token function\">add</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--dev</span> typescript @types/react @types/node eslint eslint-config-next</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"3-packagejson에-script-추가하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-packagejson%EC%97%90-script-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"3 packagejson에 script 추가하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. package.json에 script 추가하기</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code> 파일에 다음을 추가한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token property\">\"scripts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"dev\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"next dev\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"build\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"next build\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"start\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"next start\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"lint\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"next lint\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"4-public-pages-폴더-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-public-pages-%ED%8F%B4%EB%8D%94-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"4 public pages 폴더 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. public, pages 폴더 생성</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">pages</code> 파일 이름에 기반하여 라우팅 기능을 제공한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">public</code> 이미지, 폰트와 같은 static asset들을 저장하는 공간이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"5-pages-폴더에-_apptsx-파일-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-pages-%ED%8F%B4%EB%8D%94%EC%97%90-_apptsx-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"5 pages 폴더에 _apptsx 파일 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. pages 폴더에 _app.tsx 파일 생성</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">_app.tsx</code>에서는 컴포넌트 공통적으로 적용되는 레이아웃이나 상태 등을 적용할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">MyApp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Component<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> pageProps <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Component <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>pageProps<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> MyApp<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이외에도 <code class=\"language-text\">_document.tsx</code>나 <code class=\"language-text\">_error.tsx</code> 등을 생성할 수 있는데, 각 파일에 대한 설명은 <a href=\"https://beside-lab.tistory.com/entry/Nextjs-App-Document-Error\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">이 글</a>을 참고하면 좋을 것 같다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"6-gitignore-설정️\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-gitignore-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95%EF%B8%8F\" aria-label=\"6 gitignore 설정️ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. .gitignore 설정❗️</h3>\n<p>이거 까먹고 설정 안 하면 깃허브 레포지토리에 <code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code> 통째로 올라간다…<br>\n어떻게 아냐구요? 나도 알고 싶지 않았음…</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">.gitignore</code>에 관한 정보는 <a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/get-started/getting-started-with-git/ignoring-files\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">여기</a>에서 볼 수 있다.</p>\n<p>아래 코드는 cna 실행 시 자동으로 만들어지는 <code class=\"language-text\">.gitignore</code> 파일 형태다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># dependencies</span>\n/node_modules\n/.pnp\n.pnp.js\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># testing</span>\n/coverage\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># next.js</span>\n/.next/\n/out/\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># production</span>\n/build\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># misc</span>\n.DS_Store\n*.pem\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># debug</span>\nnpm-debug.log*\nyarn-debug.log*\nyarn-error.log*\n.pnpm-debug.log*\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># local env files</span>\n.env*.local\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># vercel</span>\n.vercel</code></pre></div>\n<p>나는 아래와같이 지금 당장 필요해 보이는 것들만 추가했다!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># dependencies</span>\n/node_modules\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># next.js</span>\n/.next/\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># production</span>\n/build\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># misc</span>\n.DS_Store\n*.pem\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># local env files</span>\n.env*.local\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"7-eslintrcjson\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#7-eslintrcjson\" aria-label=\"7 eslintrcjson permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>7. .eslintrc.json</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn lint</code> 명령어를 실행하면 아래 파일이 자동으로 생성된다.\n아래는 Next.js에서 권장하는 설정 방식이다. 다른 옵션은 <a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/basic-features/eslint\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">공식 문서</a>를 참고하면 된다!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"extends\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"next/core-web-vitals\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#\" aria-label=\" permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>??</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn dev</code> 실행 후 <code class=\"language-text\">next-env.d.ts</code> 파일이 생성되는데 이건 몰까.\n<a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/basic-features/typescript\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Next.js 공식 문서 </a>를 찾아보자!</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A file named <code class=\"language-text\">next-env.d.ts</code> will be created in the root of your project. This file ensures Next.js types are picked up by the TypeScript compiler. You cannot remove it or edit it as it can change at any time.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Instead of editing <code class=\"language-text\">next-env.d.ts</code>, you can include additional types by adding a new file e.g. <code class=\"language-text\">additional.d.ts</code> and then referencing it in the <code class=\"language-text\">include</code> array in your <code class=\"language-text\">tsconfig.json</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>… 그렇다고 한다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"error\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#error\" aria-label=\"error permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Error</h2>\n<h3 id=\"에러\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC\" aria-label=\"에러 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>에러</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn dev</code> 명령어를 실행했더니 다음과 같은 에러 발생</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">Option <span class=\"token string\">'--resolveJsonModule'</span> cannot be specified without <span class=\"token string\">'node'</span> module resolution strategy.</code></pre></div>\n<p>구글링하니 vscode 종료했다 다시 켜면 된다는데 난 그래도 해결 안 됨…</p>\n<h3 id=\"해결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"해결 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>해결</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">tsconfig.json</code> 파일에 다음을 추가하면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"compilerOptions\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"moduleResolution\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"node\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://typescript-kr.github.io/pages/module-resolution.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">모듈 해석 전략</a> 글을 보면 <code class=\"language-text\">classic</code>과 <code class=\"language-text\">node</code> 두 가지 값이 있다는데, <a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/tsconfig#moduleResolution\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">이 글</a>을 읽어 보니 <code class=\"language-text\">classic</code>은 최근에 잘 사용하지 않는 것 같다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"-끝-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EB%81%9D-\" aria-label=\" 끝  permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✨ 끝! ✨</h2>\n<p>CNA로 프로젝트를 생성하는 게 확실히 더 간편하겠지만, 이번 기회를 통해 프로젝트의 세부 사항들을 꼼꼼히 살펴볼 수 있었다. CRA 없이 개발 환경 구축하는 게 더 복잡해 보이던데 다음에는 그걸 시도해 봐야겠다~! 😁</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"참고-자료\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0-%EC%9E%90%EB%A3%8C\" aria-label=\"참고 자료 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고 자료</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/getting-started\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Next.js Docs - Getting Started</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/basic-features/eslint\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Next.js Docs - ESLint</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/basic-features/typescript\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Next.js Docs - TypeScript</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/get-started/getting-started-with-git/ignoring-files\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Github Docs - Ignoring files</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/tsconfig#moduleResolution\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">TypeScript Docs - Modules</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://typescript-kr.github.io/pages/module-resolution.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">TypeScript-Handbook - Module Resolution Strategies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://beside-lab.tistory.com/entry/Nextjs-App-Document-Error\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Next.js - _app.js, _document.js, _error.js에 대해 알아보자</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Next + TypeScript 개발 환경 구축하기","summary":"최근들어 CRA나 CNA를 사용하지 않고 개발환경을 직접 구축해 보고 싶은 마음이 생겼다. 그래서 create-next-app을 사용하지 않고 직접 next + ts 개발환경을 세팅해 보자!","date":"July 29, 2022","categories":["next"]}}}]},"file":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/bbf83/profile-image.jpg","srcSet":"/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/a8e5a/profile-image.jpg 30w,\n/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/bea51/profile-image.jpg 60w,\n/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/bbf83/profile-image.jpg 120w,\n/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/7793c/profile-image.jpg 240w","sizes":"(min-width: 120px) 120px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/2b147/profile-image.webp 30w,\n/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/caa3b/profile-image.webp 60w,\n/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/b15f9/profile-image.webp 120w,\n/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/b5014/profile-image.webp 240w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 120px) 120px, 100vw"}]},"width":